---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | Staticfish" description="Terms of Service for Staticfish web development services.">
  <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col overflow-x-hidden">
    <Header />
    <main class="flex-1 pt-32">
        
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
            
            <div class="mb-16">
                <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">Legal</span>
                <h1 class="text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-900 sm:text-6xl mb-6">
                  Terms of Service
                </h1>
                <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium">Last updated: January 2025</p>
            </div>

            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-600">
                
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    By engaging Staticfish for web development services, you agree to these Terms of Service. If you don't agree with any part of these terms, please don't use my services.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">2. Services Provided</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-4">I offer the following web development services:</p>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Static website development</li>
                    <li>CMS-enabled website development</li>
                    <li>E-commerce website development</li>
                    <li>Custom web application development</li>
                    <li>Website maintenance and support</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">3. Pricing and Payment</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">Pricing Structure:</strong></p>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>All prices are listed in GBP (£)</li>
                    <li>Website development fees are one-time payments</li>
                    <li>Hosting fees (£50/month) are recurring</li>
                    <li>Maintenance plans are monthly subscriptions</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">Payment Terms:</strong></p>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>50% deposit required to begin work</li>
                    <li>Remaining 50% due before website launch</li>
                    <li>Payments processed via Stripe</li>
                    <li>Invoices provided for all transactions</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">4. Project Scope and Revisions</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">What's Included:</strong></p>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Design mockups for approval before development</li>
                    <li>Up to 2 rounds of revisions at each stage</li>
                    <li>Mobile-responsive design</li>
                    <li>Basic SEO optimization</li>
                    <li>Training on content management (if applicable)</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">Scope Changes:</strong></p>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    If you request changes outside the agreed scope, I'll provide a separate quote. Major changes after development begins may delay the timeline and incur additional costs.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">5. Timeline</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-4">Typical project timelines:</p>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Static Site: 1-2 weeks</li>
                    <li>CMS Site: 2-3 weeks</li>
                    <li>E-commerce: 3-4 weeks</li>
                    <li>Custom projects: As quoted</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    Timelines assume prompt feedback from you. Delays in providing content, feedback, or approvals will extend the timeline.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">6. Content and Assets</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">Your Responsibilities:</strong></p>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Provide all text content</li>
                    <li>Provide images, logos, and brand assets</li>
                    <li>Ensure you have rights to use all provided materials</li>
                    <li>Provide domain access if using existing domain</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    If you need help with content creation or stock images, let me know and I can provide a separate quote.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">Ownership:</strong></p>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>You own the final website and all custom code created for you</li>
                    <li>I retain the right to use the project in my portfolio</li>
                    <li>I may reuse general coding patterns and techniques</li>
                    <li>Third-party tools and services remain property of their respective owners</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">8. Hosting and Maintenance</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">Hosting:</strong></p>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Hosting is provided via Cloudflare's global CDN</li>
                    <li>Includes SSL certificate, backups, and security monitoring</li>
                    <li>Monthly fee of £50 covers standard hosting</li>
                    <li>You can cancel hosting with 30 days notice</li>
                    <li>If you cancel, I'll provide your website files to move elsewhere</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">Maintenance Plans:</strong></p>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Optional for Static Site owners</li>
                    <li>Included for CMS and E-commerce clients</li>
                    <li>Covers security updates, backups, and minor changes</li>
                    <li>Cancel anytime with 30 days notice</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">9. Refunds and Cancellations</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">Before Work Begins:</strong></p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Full refund of deposit if cancelled before work starts</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">After Work Begins:</strong></p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>If design phase complete: 50% refund</li>
                    <li>If development has started: No refund, but you receive all work completed</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    I want you to be happy with the result. If there are issues, I'll work with you to resolve them.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">10. Support</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    I offer email support for all clients. Response time is typically within 24 hours during business days. For urgent issues, maintenance plan clients get priority support.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">11. Limitation of Liability</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    While I strive for excellence, I'm not liable for: loss of profits, business interruption, data loss, or any indirect damages. My total liability is limited to the amount you paid for services.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">12. Governing Law</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    These terms are governed by the laws of England and Wales. Any disputes will be resolved in the courts of England and Wales.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">13. Changes to Terms</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    I may update these terms from time to time. I'll notify clients of significant changes. Continued use of services after changes constitutes acceptance.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">14. Contact</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    Questions about these terms? Contact me:
                </p>
                
                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl mb-12">
                    <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Staticfish</p>
                    <p>Email: contact@staticfish.co.uk</p>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </main>
    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
